SELECT CONCAT(d.first_name,' ',d.last_name) AS driver, l.ticket, l.carried, l.id_order, l.placa, l.nid_driver, od.percentage, l.flete, l.updated_at FROM loads l
INNER JOIN orders o ON o.id_order=l.id_order
INNER JOIN order_details od ON od.id_order=o.id_order
INNER JOIN drivers d ON l.nid_driver=d.nid_driver
WHERE l.id_product=od.id_product and l.status=2 and date(l.updated_at)>='2020-07-20' and date(l.updated_at)<='2020-07-20'
ORDER BY  l.id_order DESC
